      <head>Berta Türtscher (<hi rend="italic">née</hi> Kathrein)</head>
      <div>

        <p>Hotel proprietor in <ref cRef="entity-002292">Galtür</ref>, in the Austrian Tyrol. </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <head>Biographical summary</head>
        <p>Born Berta Kathrein, she was the daughter of a schoolteacher. In 1925 she married <ref
            cRef="entity-002929">Franz Türtscher</ref>, with whom she took over the Gasthaus <ref
            cRef="entity-002933">Rössle</ref> in 1926. The couple had several children. Her husband
          met with a fatal accident in 1963, but she lived on into her 90s. </p>
      </div>

    </body>

